-- ArcelorMittal South Africa Returns to Profit Following Year-Earlier Loss
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-07-28T05:08:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-28/arcelormittal-south-africa-returns-to-profit-following-year-earlier-loss.html

          
          
             ArcelorMittal South Africa Ltd.
posted a first-half profit of 1.78 billion rand compared with a
year-earlier loss of 848 million rand.  
          
          


  


        